quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  11,72,is ne kaha ae hai mere bacha hoga? mein to budiya hon aur mere miyan bhi boorhay hain. yeh to barri ajeeb baat hai
  11,73,unhon ne kahakiya tum khuda ki qudrat se taajjub karti ho? ae ahal beeet tum par khuda ki rehmat aur is ki barkaten hain. woh sazawar tareef aur bzrgwar hai
  11,74,jab ibrahim se khauf jata raha aur un ko khushkhabri bhi mil gayi to qoum Loot ke baray mein lagey hum se behas karne
  11,75,"be shak ibrahim barray tahhaamul walay, naram dil aur rujoo karne walay they"
  11,76,ae ibrahim is baat ko jaane do. tumahray perwar-digaar ka hukum aap_hncha hai. aur un logon par azaab anay wala hai jo kabhi nahi talnay ka
  11,77,aur jab hamaray farishtay Loot ke paas aeye to woh un ( ke anay ) se ghumnaak aur tang dil hue aur kehnay lagey ke aaj ka din barri mushkil ka din hai
  11,78,"aur Loot ki qoum ke log un ke paas be thaasha dorrtay hue aeye aur yeh log pehlay hi se feal شنیعkiya karte they. Loot ne kaha ke ae qoum! yeh ( jo ) meri ( qoum ki ) larkiyan hain, yeh tumahray liye ( jaaiz aur ) pak hain. to khuda se daro aur mere mehmanon ke ( baray ) mein meri aabaroo nah کھوؤ.kiya tum mein koi bhi shaista aadmi nahi"
  11,79,woh bolay tum ko maloom hai ke tumhari ( qoum ki ) baityon ki hamein kuch haajat nahi. aur jo hamari gharz hai usay tum ( khoob ) jantay ho
  11,80,Loot ne kaha ae kash mujh mein tumahray muqablay ki taaqat hoti ya kisi mazboot qilay mein panah pakar sakta
  11,81,firshton ne kaha ke Loot hum tumahray perwar-digaar ke farishtay hain. yeh log hargiz tum taq nahi poanch saken ge to kuch raat rahay se apne ghar walon ko le kar chal do aur tum mein se koi shakhs peechay phir kar nah dekhe. magar tumhari biwi ke jo aafat un par parney wali hai wohi is par parre gi. un ke ( azaab ke ) waday ka waqt subah hai. aurkiya subah kuch daur hai ?
